We celebrated 10 years of our Summerville office Wednesday evening at Ashley River Park, one of our team’s most notable projects. It was a great night with clients and friends, live music, and plenty of moments that made the milestone feel extra special as we continue building on everything this team has accomplished. Celebrating our people, our achievements, and the Summerville community that’s been such a big part of it all.

