A lot has changed at Cherokee Commerce Center 85.

Concrete tilt panels are up, and steel is being erected. The 745,000-square-foot expansion of Building 2 is quickly taking shape in Gaffney, S.C.

Once complete, the 1.3 million-square-foot facility will support First Solar’s manufacturing operations and create more than 600 jobs.

More updates to come.

